t-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3. Lắp ráp, tra dầu các bộ phận bằng dầu chuyên dụng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;4. Cân bằng sai số bằng máy đo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;5. Thay thế các chi tiết zoăng, núm, đảm bảo độ kín nước&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: baseline; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 18px;