; thể t&#236;m được một mẫu đồng hồ n&#224;o th&#237;ch hợp\r\nhơn Olympia Star.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/3.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/3.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/3.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-right-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top:20%; margin-top: 0px;color:#292929;width:50%">\r\n<h3 class="headline">C&#244;ng nghệ mạ PVD </h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p>C&#244;ng nghệ mạ bằng phương ph&#225;p bốc hơi vật l&#253; b&#225;m tụ bề mặt PVD cho ph&#233;p\r\ntạo ra những bề mặt c&#243; m&#224;u sắc s&#225;ng tạo v&#224; độ bền đẹp vượt trội. Lớp mạ niken\r\nph&#237;a trong tạo độ cứng v&#224; m&#224;u sắc trung thực của bề mặt. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/5.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/5.jpg?crop=0,0,550,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/5.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-dark-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<header style="top: 20%; width:50%;margin-left:\r\n15px;">\r\n<h3 class="headline"> Trang sức d&#224;nh\r\ncho ph&#225;i nữ</h3>\r\n<div class="caption">\r\n<div align="justify">\r\n<p> L&#224; sự kết hợp giữa vẻ đẹp quyến rũ\r\ncủa m&#243;n đồ nữ trang v&#224; nghệ thuật chế t&#225;c đồng hồ đặc biệt, chiếc OPA28023LK T thực sự\r\nl&#224; thứ đồ trang sức đầy nữ t&#237;nh v&#224; duy&#234;n d&#225;ng.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/6.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/6.jpg?crop=580,0,1099,0" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/ctsp/OPA28023LKT/6.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<section class="content-block full-bleed-light-center-text">\r\n<div class="wrapper">\r\n<div class="content">\r\n<div class="default-content">\r\n<div class="visuals">\r\n<div class="images">\r\n<img class="img-responsive" alt="Bao-hiem-dong-ho" src="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_Opstar.jpg" data-crop="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_opstar_mob.jpg" data-org="image/catalog/products/2014/PK_opstar.jpg" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n', '', 'OPA28023LK T', '', ''),
